def data_viewer(data):
    
    print("\033[4m")
    print(' 5  :')
    print("\033[0m")
    display(data.sample(5))
    
    print("\033[4m")
    print('Describe:')
    print("\033[0m")    
    display(data.describe())
    
    print("\033[4m")
    print('Info:')
    print("\033[0m")  
    display(data.info())
    
    print("\033[4m")
    print(' :')
    print("\033[0m")
    display(pd.DataFrame(round(data.isna().mean()*100,1)).style.background_gradient('coolwarm'))
    
    print("\033[4m")
    print('    :')
    print("\033[0m")
    display(data.duplicated().sum())

def make_grid_search(model, param_grid, features_train, target_train):
    pipe = Pipeline([('preprocessing', transformer), ('model', model)])
    grid_search = GridSearchCV(pipe, param_grid=param_grid, cv=5, scoring='roc_auc', verbose=2)

    model_grid = grid_search.fit(features_train, target_train)
    
    print(f"  :")
    print(grid_search.best_params_)
    print('-'*10)
    print(f" ROC_AUC : {grid_search.best_score_:.3f}")

    return model_grid
